tr.td: ANC.DT.25 Anaemia, iron and folic acid supplementation

div.p: Testing for anaemia is recommended for all pregnant women. Regardless of test results, iron and folic acid supplementation is recommended. The amount of iron and folic acid supplementation will vary depending on anaemia diagnosis, population prevalence of anaemia, and whether the woman has side-effects due to iron and folic acid supplementation.
